577
00:36:24,920 --> 00:36:27,957
-I do.
-I'd toss out that Bible if I were you.

578
00:36:28,080 --> 00:36:31,231
-Your Honor.
-Inspector Speight, please.

579
00:36:34,880 --> 00:36:38,634
Miss Mallon, can you tell me
how you came to be at this hearing today?

580
00:36:38,800 --> 00:36:40,677
I was kidnapped.

581
00:36:40,800 --> 00:36:43,360
Not for ransom, but I was attacked.

582
00:36:43,440 --> 00:36:46,591
Taken from me job
and shut away by these awful people

583
00:36:46,680 --> 00:36:48,636
who think I'm some sort of monster.

584
00:36:48,720 --> 00:36:51,632
A devil. Those people.

585
00:36:51,720 --> 00:36:54,280
Maligning me in the papers.

586
00:36:54,360 --> 00:36:56,555
Calling me Typhoid Mary.

587
00:36:56,640 --> 00:36:59,552
