625
00:39:20,680 --> 00:39:22,875
She has had one a week
for the last four months,

626
00:39:22,960 --> 00:39:24,359
so that's 16 in total.

627
00:39:24,440 --> 00:39:26,032
You should ask him
how many of those tests

628
00:39:26,120 --> 00:39:27,633
