629
00:39:27,760 --> 00:39:30,149
Miss Mallon, please.

630
00:39:32,320 --> 00:39:34,038
How many, Dr. Chickering?

631
00:39:34,120 --> 00:39:37,635
There were five instances where the disease
was not found in a sample.

632
00:39:38,680 --> 00:39:41,274
Well, it makes one
wonder if it is your test

633
00:39:41,360 --> 00:39:43,555
